## Why Look for HockeyStack Alternatives?

HockeyStack is a strong B2B attribution platform—all-in-one, fast to deploy, with LinkedIn impression tracking. But it's not for everyone. (Full disclosure: mbuzz is one of the alternatives we cover. If you want an all-in-one platform with web analytics, surveys, and fast deployment bundled together, HockeyStack does that well—we'll help you decide.)

**Common reasons to explore alternatives:**

| Limitation | Impact |
|------------|--------|
| **Expensive** | $2,200+/mo starting, increasing with traffic |
| **All-in-one or nothing** | Bundled analytics you may not need |
| **No model flexibility** | Can't validate if attribution is accurate |
| **Enterprise limitations** | Data governance, access controls, scale issues reported |
| **Vendor lock-in** | Deep integration makes switching costly |

If any of these resonate, here are your best options.

