## 2. Dreamdata — Best for Budget-Conscious B2B

**Why consider Dreamdata:** Similar B2B focus, transparent pricing, free tier available.

### Dreamdata vs HockeyStack

| Factor | HockeyStack | Dreamdata |
|--------|-------------|-----------|
| Free tier | ✗ No | ✓ Yes (Individual) |
| Team pricing | $2,200+/mo | $999/mo |
| Setup time | ~2 weeks | 4-8 weeks |
| Journey visualization | Good | Excellent |
| All-in-one | Yes | No |
| LinkedIn impressions | ✓ Yes | Limited |

### Why Dreamdata Over HockeyStack

Dreamdata offers the core B2B attribution capabilities at roughly half the price, with a free tier to start. The tradeoff: slower setup and no bundled analytics.

### Best For

- B2B teams with budget constraints
- Those wanting to try before buying (free tier)
- Teams focused on journey visualization
- Companies that don't need all-in-one

**Also consider:** [Dreamdata alternatives](/articles/dreamdata-alternatives) for other mid-market options.

